// Slice 13: Join Operator
// Feature: Join two tables by matching values on a key column.

// Basic join:
T1 | join (T2) on Key

// Join with kind:
T1 | join kind=inner (T2) on Key

// Left outer join:
StormEvents | join kind=leftouter (PopulationData) on State

// The parser handles join loosely — it consumes all tokens between
// join and the next pipe, so complex join syntax is accepted.
